OL,3,COpen the door! First female Black Rod
OL,4,Cconfirms she's leaving Parliament
OL,6,FThe world's most-famous door-knocker
OL,7,Fhas confirmed she is standing down as
OL,8,FBlack Rod.
OL,10,FSarah Clarke - the first woman to hold
OL,11,Fthe role in its 670-year history -
OL,12,Fwill leave Parliament in the summer
OL,13,Fafter almost eight years in post.
OL,15,FAs Black Rod, Ms Clarke has become
OL,16,Fknown around the world as the person
OL,17,Fwho knocks on the door of the House of
OL,18,FCommons to inform them of the state
OL,19,Fopening of Parliament - and
OL,20,Fsubsequently has the door slammed in
OL,21,Fher face.
