OL,6,FFew people would say having a door
OL,7,Fshut on them is the "greatest honour
OL,8,Fand privilege of my life", but perhaps
OL,9,Fthat would change if they were
OL,10,Fknocking on behalf of royalty.
OL,12,FSince being appointed by Queen
OL,13,FElizabeth II in 2017, Ms Clarke has
OL,14,Fbeen involved in six state openings of
OL,15,FParliament, including the first
OL,16,Fdelivered by King Charles.
OL,18,FShe also organised the Queen's lying
OL,19,Fin state and was involved in her state
OL,20,Ffuneral.
