OL,3,COpen the door! First female Black Rod
OL,4,Cconfirms she's leaving Parliament
OL,6,FReflecting on her time in the role,
OL,7,Fshe said: "It has been the greatest
OL,8,Fhonour and privilege of my life to
OL,9,Fserve as Black Rod during what has
OL,10,Fbeen a most extraordinary period.
OL,12,F"I am hugely grateful to the many
OL,13,Fexceptional people I have worked
OL,14,Falongside during my term of office,
OL,15,Fwhose support in enabling me to carry
OL,16,Fout my duties has been invaluable."
OL,18,FA search to find her successor is now
OL,19,Funderway.
