OL,6,FWhat is Black Rod and why are they
OL,7,Fcalled that?
OL,9,FBlack Rod traditionally performs three
OL,10,Fformal roles - Gentleman or Lady Usher
OL,11,Fof the Black Rod, Serjeant-at-Arms in
OL,12,Fthe House of Lords and Secretary to
OL,13,Fthe Lord Great Chamberlain.
OL,15,FAt the State Opening of Parliament,
OL,16,FBlack Rod's most prominent moment in
OL,17,Fthe parliamentary calendar, Black Rod
OL,18,Fis sent from the Lords Chamber to the
OL,19,FCommons Chamber to summon MPs to hear
OL,20,Fthe Queen's Speech.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
