OL,11,FThe earliest known reference to the
OL,12,Frole of Black Rod as the Usher to the
OL,13,FOrder of the Garter is in letters
OL,14,Fpatent from 1361, which refers to
OL,15,FWalter Whitehorse performing the role.
OL,17,FWalter Whitehorse is believed to have
OL,18,Fbeen the first person to hold the
OL,19,Fpost, which 59 others have held since.
